Marquis Qinghe is in a difficult situation in the North.

24
00:02:26,530 --> 00:02:29,010
The officials and generals agreed overtly but secretly opposed.

25
00:02:29,010 --> 00:02:31,560
Your Majesty, as long as Duke Cheng is there,

