120
00:10:23,610 --> 00:10:26,260
State affairs are chaotic, everybody is protecting themselves.

121
00:10:26,260 --> 00:10:29,730
Young Master Ning is willing to play against the Imperial Court.

122
00:10:29,730 --> 00:10:33,850
On this occasion, heal the hearts of people. Time and tide wait for no man.

123
00:10:33,850 --> 00:10:38,610
Loyal servants are disappointed, treacherous servants in power, a country not stable, civilians are uneasy.

124
00:10:38,610 --> 00:10:43,150
Common people suffer, the vitality of the landscape harmed.

125
00:10:43,150 --> 00:10:45,370
I will surely do all that I can.

126
