129
00:11:11,590 --> 00:11:14,050
Your Majesty, I dare not speak casually.

130
00:11:14,050 --> 00:11:17,130
After Zhu Shan left the North, the officers and soldiers there

131
00:11:17,130 --> 00:11:22,910
