133
00:11:26,810 --> 00:11:31,980
In the past, there were indeed many memorials to impeach Zhu Shan.

134
00:11:31,980 --> 00:11:35,830
Your Majesty, the impeachment this time is not the same as before.

135
00:11:35,830 --> 00:11:39,160
The past impeachments were requested by the civil officials in the North.

136
00:11:39,160 --> 00:11:43,090
It's now from the officers and soldiers in the North.

137
00:11:43,090 --> 00:11:45,510
I haven't been willing to submit the memorials.

138
00:11:45,510 --> 00:11:49,200
One, I didn't believe that Zhu Shan would be that bold and reckless.

139
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:53,370
Second, Your Majesty rewarded him handsomely.

140
00:11:53,370 --> 00:11:55,820
Hence, I privately conducted a secret investigation.

141
00:11:55,820 --> 00:11:58,440
In the end, I unraveled more.

142
00:11:58,440 --> 00:12:04,080
Zhu Shan became more arrogant and instigated the two countries.

143
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:07,490
I dare not hide it anymore.

144
00:12:13,320 --> 00:12:15,620
No, no, no.

145
00:12:15,620 --> 00:12:18,760
Duke Cheng is a military commander that the late emperor relied heavily upon,

146
00:12:18,760 --> 00:12:23,440
and a person of good morals and reputation. I don't believe this.

147
00:12:23,440 --> 00:12:29,110
Your Majesty, I have evidence of Zhu Shan's crimes. Please take a look.

148
00:12:40,490 --> 00:12:45,000
Your Majesty, this is the correspondence between Zhu Shan and the Crown Prince of Northern Qi.

149
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:50,750
